Our Story
/$
$
A North Port hidden gem! Sharks Fish House is an award winning local, family owned restaurant that has been serving the community for 23 years. We take pride in offering the freshest seafood and a unique dining experience that keeps our customers coming back for more. Our team is dedicated to providing exceptional service and creating a welcoming atmosphere for everyone who walks through our doors.
